Fix a batch of small correctness bugs: `Qobj.logm` now reports "logm" in its non-square error, `HEOMResult.final_ado_state` returns the ADO state instead of the density matrix, `MCSolver.StateFeedback` forwards `prop` and uses ket dimensions, `qdiags` no longer marks sub-unit-modulus diagonals as unitary, `qzero`/`qzero_like` no longer mark non-square operators as Hermitian, and the scipy lsoda excess-work message has a missing space restored.
